// V.34.12: SLIP REPLAY POOL helpers (CNX regression — Snippet 2 V.34.10 companion)
// Purpose: re-upload of an identical slip binary should not spam Slip2Go quota —
//          reuse the cached response to either (a) confirm prior payment,
//          (b) replay our processing if we failed mid-flow, or (c) defer to admin.
